HAVE ALREADY BEEN MADE.

12:57.208 --> 12:58.166
[CHUCKLES]

13:00.959 --> 13:03.500
GET A HOLD OF YOURSELF,
JENNIFER.

13:03.500 --> 13:05.917
I'M SORRY.
