13:05.917 --> 13:08.917
WHAT WAS THAT
THAT YOU WERE DOING
WITH THE KISSING?

13:08.917 --> 13:14.166
WHY DID YOU--YOUNG LADY,
DO YOU HAVE A BOYFRIEND?

13:14.166 --> 13:16.125
CLIFF, ARE YOU
MY GRAMS' BOYFRIEND?

13:16.125 --> 13:19.291
JENNIFER,
I DON'T THINK--
YES, I AM.

13:19.291 --> 13:20.417
I THINK.
AREN'T I?

13:20.417 --> 13:24.125
YES. YES, YOU ARE.

13:24.125 --> 13:26.166
OH, MY GOODNESS! WHY--

13:26.166 --> 13:27.625
DID THIS
JUST SLIP YOUR MIND?

13:27.625 --> 13:29.834
IS THIS
SOMETHING THAT YOU JUST
FORGOT TO MENTION TO ME?

13:29.834 --> 13:32.000
SHOULD CLIFTON AND I
LEAVE YOU TWO ALONE
FOR A MINUTE?

13:32.000 --> 13:33.250
'CAUSE
WE CAN DO THAT.

13:33.250 --> 13:34.375
CLIFF, WHAT DO YOU DO?

13:34.375 --> 13:35.750
YOU'VE GOT
TO BE KIDDING!

13:35.750 --> 13:40.041
